videos.description: Kentucky's Nick Richards begins a momentous sequence with a putback stuff and ferocious block that leads to a Tyler Herro transition 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Richards' vicious block leads to transition 3

videos.description: Kentucky turns defense into offense, as Tyler Herro commands the break and lobs it up to EJ Montgomery, who leaps and throws down the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Montgomery flushes fast-break alley-oop for Kentucky
